  "text": "Sequences were aligned for display using the CLU STA LW algorithm as implemented in MEGA7 [CITATION_1] . Sequence logos displayed in Fig. 2 were generated from alignments using WebLogo [CITATION_2] . Supplemental Table 1 contains sequences and accession numbers for all channels included in the sequence logos, and Supplemental Table 2 contains amino acid frequencies at each gate position for the sequence logos.",
